Checks: '*,-cert-err34-c, -clang-analyzer-security.insecureAPI.strcpy,-clang-analyzer-security.insecureAPI.DeprecatedOrUnsafeBufferHandling,-clang-diagnostic-deprecated-declarations,-readability-isolate-declaration,-cppcoreguidelines-init-variables,-misc-no-recursion,-readability-non-const-parameter'
